:0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"住醫院果陣<br />\n多菜少肉少鹽少飯<br />\n<br />\n一日三餐"},{"pid":"b469695c5dc2010702ea14ff37ad1bd54b654a52","tid":2314371,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"早餐炒蛋麵包咖啡<br />\n午餐食返之前一晚嘅晚餐<br />\n晚餐通常係pasta+菜+肉+蕃茄<br />\n視乎心情決定係放湯定乾身"},{"pid":"44632d72ea9f4cb0860c15d9336357d1375cccdb","tid":2314371,"uid":51641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b469695c5dc2010702ea14ff37ad1bd54b654a52","tid":2314371,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:07:53.000Z","msg":"早餐炒蛋麵包咖啡<br />\n午餐食返之前一晚嘅晚餐<br />\n晚餐通常係pasta+菜+肉+蕃茄<br />\n視乎心情決定係放湯定乾身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"食隔夜餸好似已經好唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b3799f8684a512080ad01e465fd9140bd32199","tid":2314371,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:39:52.000Z","msg":"每日要食25-30g纖維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一斤菜心先得9克纖維<br />\n一個橙有4.5g<br />\n點啪到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}